.TH "propulse" "1" "2026-06-10" "\[lq]Propulse Tracker 0.9.6.1\[rq] \[lq]\[rq] \[lq]2026-06-10\[rq] \[lq]General Commands Manual\[rq]" ""
.hy
.SH NAME
.PP
\f[B]propulse\f[R] - crossplatform tracker compatible with Amiga
ProTracker modules
.SH SYNOPSIS
.PP
\f[B]propulse\f[R] [\f[I]file\f[R]]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.PP
\f[B]Propulse\f[R] is a tracker for creating and playing Amiga
ProTracker compatible modules (.MOD), using an interface inspired by
Impulse Tracker and Schism Tracker.
.PP
It features a highly accurate playback engine based on 8bitbubsy\[cq]s
work, itself derived from a disassembly of the original Amiga ProTracker
firmware.
Test cases such as \f[I]black_queen.mod\f[R] and MPT test modules play
correctly.
.PP
An optional \f[I]file\f[R] argument can be passed to open a module
directly on startup.
.SH OPTIONS
.PP
\f[B]propulse\f[R] does not currently support command-line options
beyond opening a file on startup.
.SH FEATURES
.IP \[bu] 2
Familiar keyboard commands from Impulse Tracker and Schism Tracker
.IP \[bu] 2
Fully configurable keybindings, colour palettes, bitmap fonts, and
screen layouts
.IP \[bu] 2
WAV export with optional loop and fade out
.IP \[bu] 2
Integrated mouse-driven sample editor
.SH SUPPORTED FORMATS
.TP
\f[B]MOD\f[R]
Loads and saves Amiga ProTracker modules, including 15-sample Ultimate
SoundTracker mods, NoiseTracker, and PowerPacked files.
.TP
\f[B]P61A\f[R]
Imports The Player 6.1a crunched modules.
.TP
\f[B]IT\f[R], \f[B]S3M\f[R]
Imports Impulse Tracker and Scream Tracker 3 modules.
.TP
\f[B]Samples\f[R]
raw, IFF 8SVX, WAV, MP3, and Ogg Vorbis (requires BASS library).
.SH FILES
.TP
\f[I]\[ti]/.config/propulse/\f[R]
Per-user configuration directory (keybindings, colour palette,
settings).
.TP
\f[I]/usr/share/propulse/data/\f[R]
Shared data files (fonts, palettes, icons).
.SH BUGS
.PP
No known bugs.
Please report issues at <https://github.com/hukkax/Propulse/issues>.
.SH SEE ALSO
.PP
\f[B]schismtracker\f[R](1)
.SH AUTHOR
